Package CrazyChess.logic

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AI
    The class responsible for the Artificial Intelligence in our game.
    BasicValidityChecker
    This class performs some basic checks to see if a move on the board is at least somewhat valid.
    Castle
    Class for implementing castling
    ExtraChecksAndTools
    This class is used to perform some extra checks and to provide some extra tools that might be useful further in the project.
    MainLogic
    This is the main class for the chess game logic.
    Position
    This class is used to hold position of the piece on the board.
    Utilities
    Class with some utilities for getting pieces from and placing pieces to game states
